<headline>Special Weather Statement issued October 07 at 7:02AM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Patchy dense fog this morning...
Patchy dense fog will affect portions of North Central and
Southwest MT this morning, especially in low-lying areas like
river valleys. The fog will reduce visibility to near a quarter
of a mile at times. The fog will diminish around mid morning.
Those traveling this morning should be alert for quickly changing
visibility. Slow down and use low beam headlights when traveling
through fog.</description>
